title: The Townhall Weekend Journal for JULY-12-2013 FRI
description:
Egypt Erupts...Again



Friday, July 12, 2013




Egypt Erupts...Again
Weekend Journal
Hugh Hewitt discussed the turmoil in Egypt with military historian Max Boot.
 Hewitt also spoke with Pulitzer Prize winning journalist John Burns about Egypt.

 Bill Bennett discussed the Obamacare disaster with James Capretta, senior fellow at the Ethics and Public Policy Center.

 Dennis Prager on the transgender mess in California schools.

 Bill Bennett spoke with Maggie Gallagher, author of The Case for Marriage.

 Prager on the San Francisco airplane crash.
